this song shakes my whole being... it's been two years that I have listened it again...but again, like always, it makes me shiver with a  piercing passion...leaving with goosebumps (especially during the aalap) ...it runs like blood in my veins...and takes me to a different world. It compelled me to comment here. 
This song would be dedicated to the love of my life who I hope to meet one day. 
Papon, you're the finest singer we have and going to be my lifelong favourite. Such a lovesick(lovestruck) voice and compostion!

With love,
Bhakti
